<section class="client-satisfaction">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="satisfaction__content">
      <h2 class="satisfaction__title">Our Client Satisfaction</h2>
      
      <div class="satisfaction__text-group">
        <p class="satisfaction__text">
          Creating a valuable experience and a beautiful finished product for our clients is 
          what Lake County Outdoors values most. That's why we communicate efficiently, work 
          to understand the needs of our customers, and deliver the best results.
        </p>
        
        <p class="satisfaction__text">
          We offer services to a diverse range of clients, including major retailers, and 
          essential service providers like schools, public institutions, and residential homes.
        </p>
        
        <p class="satisfaction__text">
          Our commitment to excellence and professionalism ensures safe and accessible 
          environments for customers and employees, all while getting the job done in the 
          best and most efficient way.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="satisfaction__experience">
        <h3 class="satisfaction__subtitle">Our Experience</h3>
        <p class="satisfaction__text">
          We service a wide range of properties, from residential lots to expansive malls 
          and Fortune 100 corporate headquarters, handling diverse projects with precision 
          and efficiency.
        </p>
        <p class="satisfaction__highlight">
          Choose Lake County Outdoors, LLC for tailored solutions to meet all your 
          commercial property needs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .client-satisfaction {
    background-color: var(--white);
    padding: var(--space-12) 0;
  }
  
  .satisfaction__content {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .satisfaction__title {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
  }
  
  .satisfaction__text-group {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }
  
  .satisfaction__text {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--neutral-dark);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .satisfaction__experience {
    background-color: var(--neutral-light);
    padding: var(--space-8);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .satisfaction__subtitle {
    color: var(--secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
  }
  
  .satisfaction__highlight {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .client-satisfaction {
      padding: var(--space-16) 0;
    }
    
    .satisfaction__text {
      text-align: left;
    }
    
    .satisfaction__experience {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .client-satisfaction {
      padding: var(--space-20) 0;
    }
  }
</style>